== Touch (hand symbol) == {{Quote|There's a grate on top of the aquarium; I can't fit my hands through.}}
== Look (eye symbol) == {{Quote|Why there are people in the world who are soothed by stupidly gaping at fishes, I will never ... Wait a sec, there's something sparkly over there! Besides few fish, there's a key swimming around in there.}}
